ncrease statistical power, and combine phylogenic history and functional traits of plant species with the type and traits of mycorrhizal fungi to better understand how plant-microbe interactions influence biogeochemical cycling in the rhizosphere. {\textcopyright} 2018 Elsevier Ltd},
