t N forms in soil was identified as a key mechanism by which beech alters soil N cycling with potential positive feedbacks on its acquisition by the plant. Our result emphasizes the importance of considering within-species litter-trait variability in litter decomposition. {\textcopyright} 2016 The Authors. Journal of Ecology {\textcopyright} 2016 British Ecological Society},
